{"word":"ἀνθίζω","slug":"ἀνθίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνθίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἄνθος</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to strew</i> or <i>deck with flowers</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to dye with bright colour</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἠνθισμένος</el> <i>dyed, disguised</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}